<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA85">
<l>paṭikaṇ ṭaṟitiyē pāmpaṇaiyi ṉāṉpuṭ</l>
<l>koṭikaṇ ṭaṟitiyē kūṟāy – vaṭiviṟ</l>
<l>poṟiyaintu muḷḷaṭakkip pōtoṭunī rēnti</l>
<l>neṟiniṉṟa neñcamē nī</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Can you see [and] know [his] body? Can you see [and] know</l>
<l>the bird banner of him on the snake bed? Speak, you,</l>
<l>oh heart that controls the five senses inside the body, offers water</l>
<l>along with buds [and] stays on the path.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
